{"tid":844691,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"提吓人都俾人閪面。。。","createTime":"2018-10-02T05:24:23.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-02T05:39:54.000Z","uid":90457,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"0bb29f8e696d33fcedad165e675648b6e5c0683d","tid":844691,"uid":90457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T05:24:23.000Z","msg":"喺七仔排隊買嘢，排我前面個阿嬸右肩孭住個袋，袋裡面有隻松鼠狗<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n不過就見到成條狗繩跌出嚟，而隻狗本身就箍住，我就好禮貌噉提吓個阿嬸<br />\n<br />\n「唔好意思呀，條繩跌咗出嚟，有啲人行路唔帶眼一踩到就會扯傷『佢』」，而我就怕冒犯到佢，「太太」「小姐」呢啲字都冇用過，雖則佢睇落都有六十<br />\n<br />\n點知個阿嬸聽到之後，嗰種蔑視嘅目光直頭好似係用眼神叫我「死撚開」，然後嗱嗱聲收好條狗繩（收完都係成條跌落嚟）<br />\n<br />\n仆你個街真係好戇鳩，我講我呀，提完佢條狗繩最後都係跌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n本身見佢個嘴臉都好難睇好睇唔起人，提佢都係多餘，縱使我都唔預佢會講聲唔該，但係使唔使用呢啲態度嚟對人呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2d977f348c3b7d779f10cc8d20c1347e622fb6f","tid":844691,"uid":21423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T05:25:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"21ea680257dd345ef471372b42cae67cccd3c604","tid":844691,"uid":90457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d2d977f348c3b7d779f10cc8d20c1347e622fb6f","tid":844691,"uid":21423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T05:25:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T05:26:06.000Z","msg":"生閪閉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c5c17c055b16d8e96902a132b704c8d36081fc0","tid":844691,"uid":21423,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T05:26:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a6d1e02e8b37b86b5c13aca089770390eab99110","tid":844691,"uid":85751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T05:28:40.000Z","msg":"你柒"},{"pid":"90fa62012430dfa490e1bfa8eb3